      "description": "Get ready for a rewarding project! This vehicle is in poor condition and will need some dedicated TLC to get back to its best, but it offers a fantastic opportunity for a mechanic or DIY enthusiast looking for a budget-friendly start. It\u2019s an honest car with plenty of potential for someone ready to put in the work!",
