      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint condition and presents as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish, free of any stone chips, scratches, or dings. Inside, the cabin is immaculate, with the leather upholstery still firm and the original factory scent preserved. It has been meticulously garage-kept and professionally detailed, with a full service history documenting its perfect upkeep. This is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade example that needs absolutely nothing.",
