    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver. While the engine and transmission are functional, the car shows noticeable cosmetic wear including some minor scratches on the body and visible thinning of the upholstery inside. It has been maintained regularly, though it lacks the polish of a newer model and may require some minor upcoming maintenance for non-essential components. It is a solid, honest car for someone looking for dependable transportation at a reasonable price.",
