    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Offered here is a truly exceptional, showroom-quality vehicle that stands as a testament to meticulous ownership. This car has been exclusively garage-kept in a climate-controlled environment and has never seen inclement weather. The exterior finish is absolutely flawless, featuring deep, mirror-like paint with a professional-grade ceramic coating and zero rock chips or door dings. The alloy wheels are pristine, with no curb rash, wrapped in high-performance tires with nearly full tread remaining. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather upholstery remains supple and tight, free from any creases or wear marks, and the interior still retains its new-car fragrance. Every technological feature, sensor, and button operates with factory precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, boasting a documented service history performed strictly by master technicians using OEM parts. The engine bay is clean enough to eat off of, and the undercarriage shows no signs of road debris or oxidation. This is a rare find for a buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
